          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The cross  section  of  the  16O(g,n)  reaction  were",
                " measured with tagged photons of  50  -  70  MeV  and",
                " cpmpared with  the  equivalent  (g,p)  reaction  and",
                " various theoretical calculations.  The  implications",
                " for the  dependence  of  the  (g,N) cross section on",
                " meson exchange currents and final state rescattering",
                " are discussed."
              ]
            }
          ],
